  "html": "<h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t<span>Scene</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<span>III</span>\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n\t\t\t\t<table>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tbody>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<em><b><b>Madame Pernelle</b></b>, <b>Orgon</b>, <b>Elmire</b>, <b>Cl├ęante</b>, <b>Mariane</b>, <b>Damis</b>, <b>Dorine</b>.</em>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Madame Pernelle</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>WhatÔÇÖs this? I hear of fearful mysteries!</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Orgon</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>Strange things indeed, for my own eyes to witness;</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>You see how IÔÇÖm requited for my kindness,</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>I zealously receive a wretched beggar,</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>I lodge him, entertain him like my brother,</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>Load him with benefactions every day,</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>Give him my daughter, give him all my fortune:</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>And he meanwhile, the villain, rascal, wretch,</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>Tries with black treason to suborn my wife,</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>And not content with such a foul design,</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>He dares to menace me with my own favours,</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>And would make use of those advantages</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>Which my too foolish kindness armed him with,</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>To ruin me, to take my fortune from me,</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>And leave me in the state I saved him from.</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Dorine</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>Poor man!</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Madame Pernelle</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>My son, I cannot possibly</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>Believe he could intend so black a deed.</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Orgon</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>What?</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Madame Pernelle</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>Worthy men are still the sport of envy.</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Orgon</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>Mother, what do you mean by such a speech?</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Madame Pernelle</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>There are strange goings-on about your house,</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>And everybody knows your people hate him.</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Orgon</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>WhatÔÇÖs that to do with what I tell you now?</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Madame Pernelle</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>I always said, my son, when you were little:</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>That virtue here below is hated ever;</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>The envious may die, but envy never.</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Orgon</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>WhatÔÇÖs that fine speech to do with present facts?</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Madame Pernelle</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>Be sure, theyÔÇÖve forged a hundred silly liesÔüáÔÇŐÔüáÔÇŽ</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Orgon</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>IÔÇÖve told you once, I saw it all myself.</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Madame Pernelle</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>For slanderers abound in calumniesÔüáÔÇŐÔüáÔÇŽ</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Orgon</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>Mother, youÔÇÖd make me damn my soul. I tell you</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>I saw with my own eyes his shamelessness.</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Madame Pernelle</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>Their tongues for spitting venom never lack,</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>ThereÔÇÖs nothing here below theyÔÇÖll not attack.</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Orgon</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>Your speech has not a single grain of sense.</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>I saw it, harkee, saw it, with these eyes</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>I sawÔüáÔÇödÔÇÖye know what saw means?ÔüáÔÇömust I say it</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>A hundred times, and din it in your ears?</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Madame Pernelle</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>My dear, appearances are oft deceiving,</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>And seeing shouldnÔÇÖt always be believing.</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Orgon</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>IÔÇÖll go mad.</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Madame Pernelle</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>False suspicions may delude,</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>And good to evil oft is misconstrued.</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Orgon</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>Must I construe as Christian charity</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>The wish to kiss my wife!</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Madame Pernelle</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>You must, at least,</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>Have just foundation for accusing people,</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>And wait until you see a thing for sure.</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Orgon</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>The devil! How could I see any surer?</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>Should I have waited till, before my eyes,</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>HeÔüáÔÇŐÔüáÔÇŽ No, youÔÇÖll make me say things quite improper.</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Madame Pernelle</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>In short, ÔÇÖtis known too pure a zeal inflames him;</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>And so, I cannot possibly conceive</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>That he should try to do whatÔÇÖs charged against him.</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Orgon</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>If you were not my mother, I should say</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>Such things!ÔüáÔÇŐÔüáÔÇŽ I know not what, IÔÇÖm so enraged!</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Dorine</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span><em>To <b>Orgon</b>.</em> Fortune has paid you fair, to be so doubted;</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>You flouted our report, now yours is flouted.</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Cl├ęante</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>WeÔÇÖre wasting time here in the merest trifling,</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>Which we should rather use in taking measures</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>To guard ourselves against the scoundrelÔÇÖs threats.</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Damis</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>You think his impudence could go far?</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Elmire</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>For one, I canÔÇÖt believe it possible;</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>Why, his ingratitude would be too patent.</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Cl├ęante</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>DonÔÇÖt trust to that; heÔÇÖll find abundant warrant</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>To give good colour to his acts against you;</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>And for less cause than this, a strong cabal</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>Can make oneÔÇÖs life a labyrinth of troubles.</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>I tell you once again: armed as he is</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>You never should have pushed him quite so far.</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Orgon</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>True; yet what could I do? The rascalÔÇÖs pride</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>Made me lose all control of my resentment.</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Cl├ęante</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>I wish with all my heart that some pretence</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>Of peace could be patched up between you two</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Elmire</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>If I had known what weapons he was armed with,</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>I never should have raised such an alarm,</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>And myÔüáÔÇŐÔüáÔÇŽ</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Orgon</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<em>To <b>Dorine</b>, seeing <b><abbr>Mr.</abbr>┬áLoyal</b> come in.</em>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>WhoÔÇÖs coming now? Go quick, find out.</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>IÔÇÖm in a fine state to receive a visit!</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t<section id=\"scene-5-4\">"
